{"tid":2445427,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"（生化） 滅活是如何做到的？","createTime":"2021-03-13T15:10:41.000Z","updateTime":"2021-03-13T15:58:31.000Z","uid":91648,"like":1,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"1afac85392b893b99f67b82e10552e4f3d15dc23","tid":2445427,"uid":91648,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:10:41.000Z","msg":"減毒活疫苗是通過減少病原體的毒力，<strong><span class=\"red\">但仍保持它存活的疫苗。</span></strong><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />其採用感染因子，藉由改變使病毒變的無害或降低毒性。 例如－ 病毒：麻疹疫苗、腮腺炎疫苗、風疹疫苗、減毒活流感疫苗（季節性流感噴鼻和2009年H1N1流感的鼻腔噴霧劑）、水痘疫苗、口服小兒麻痺症疫苗（薩賓）、輪狀病毒疫苗和黃熱病疫苗。而狂犬病疫苗現在是在兩個不同的減毒形式，一種用於人類，另外一個用於動物。 細菌：卡介苗、傷寒疫苗和流行性斑疹傷寒疫苗。"},{"pid":"c9947f7b2e475f100d11782eaebeec8f787cfd9a","tid":2445427,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"科興滅咗6個活啦（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_special.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"e784a7d70443a2f83aed01aa62bf27f59c8a9116","tid":2445427,"uid":196924,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:13:36.000Z","msg":"滅活同減活唔識分呀<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d0d9b8be564c5aa89013a304ffa72b908115907b","tid":2445427,"uid":279763,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c9947f7b2e475f100d11782eaebeec8f787cfd9a","tid":2445427,"uid":242537,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2021-03-13T15:13:17.000Z","msg":"科興滅咗6個活啦（好似係）<img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/gold.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/cow/power_spec